name: DESERT CRASH 2696
description:
Enjoy with care, you may get stuck in one of the infinite parallel dimensions of Desert Crash.


Interactive abstract animation with light control, zoom and rotation. Created by Zydron aka Caleb Mascarenhas using P5js.

Controls:
Mouse position or touch controls the light.
Scroll or pinch gesture controls zoom
Click and drag rotates the object

The animation fits any screen size
